# Sentiment Analysis Using NLP and Machine Learning

A Natural Language Processing (NLP) project that classifies text reviews into positive or negative sentiments using Machine Learning techniques and TF-IDF vectorization.

---

# Project Overview

This project performs sentiment analysis on textual data by applying NLP preprocessing techniques and Machine Learning algorithms. The system converts text into numerical vectors using TF-IDF and predicts sentiment labels based on trained classification models.

The project demonstrates the complete NLP workflow:

```text
Text Data
→ Preprocessing
→ TF-IDF Vectorization
→ Machine Learning Model
→ Sentiment Prediction
